snippet.title: Elevator Hitch Trailer
snippet.description:
PLAY FOR FREE NOW ON ITCH.IO
https://racheldrawsthis.itch.io/elevator-hitch

Elevator Hitch is a short 2.5D surreal/liminal horror escape room visual novel with point-and-click and puzzle elements following the story of two co-workers suddenly finding themselves stuck together in a "Perfectly Normal" 70s office elevator. 

They must explore each liminal-looking floor and find a way to
get off the elevator to their actual destinations.

Development &  Story &  Graphics 
- RachelDrawsThis 
- Ekrix

Composer & Sound Designer
- BellKalengar
